Title: Anyonic FRT construction
Authors: Shahn Majid and M.J. Rodriguez-Plaza
Comments: 11 pages, Latex, DAMTP/94-64, NIKHEF-H 94-25
\\
  The Faddeev-Reshetikhin-Takhtajan method to construct matrix bialgebras from
non-singular solutions of the quantum Yang-Baxter equation is extended to the
anyonic or $\Z_n$-graded case. The resulting anyonic quantum matrices are
braided groups in which the braiding is given by a phase factor.
